					description="Certain vehicles may not have Active protection system enabled, if you want a specific vehicle to have it, create a dummy of the vehicle you want it to apply to and then synchronize this module with the dummy vehicle. That vehicle class will now have the type of APS assigned to it." \n "" \n "Do note this dummy vehicle should be hidden from view on some corner of the map.";
